1a:T408,Internal evidence clearly describes a 2.9mm all-suture soft anchor for shoulder arthroscopic repairs. Brochure description explicitly states 'rotator cuff and Bankart repairs where bone real estate is limited,' confirming clinical indications. Material (UHMWPE) and diameter (2.9mm) are consistent with all-suture anchor construction. Entity represents a specific diameter variant within the FILAHOOK Soft Anchor System family. However, brand manufacturer appears to be Meril Life Sciences, but no external verification available to confirm FILAHOOK brand ownership or validate product specifications. Current classification shows 'Without Needle' which may indicate suture pre-loading configuration but requires verification. Missing brand confirmation and inability to verify external clinical literature necessitates manual review despite high internal evidence quality. Recommend review to: (1) confirm brand ownership, (2) verify suture configuration and needle options, (3) validate all-suture vs hybrid anchor classification.16:["$","$L19",null,{"product":{"product_name":"FILAHOOK Soft Anchor 2.9mm","product_name_display":"FILAHOOK Soft Anchor 2.9mm","sku_code":"MA-SZU00007","product_family":"FILAHOOK Soft Anchor System","product_family_display":"FILAHOOK Soft Anchor System","slug":"filahook-soft-anchor-2.9mm","images":[{"storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/spm-brochure/cover_c84c31b4.jpg","filename":"spm_cover_c84c31b4.jpg","source":"brochure_cover"}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"agile-ortho/brochures/sports-medicine-catalog.pdf","seo_meta_title":"FILAHOOK Soft Anchor 2.9mm | FILAHOOK Soft Anchor System Shoulder Arthroscopy - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"All-suture soft anchor 2.9mm. Ideal for rotator cuff and Bankart repairs where bone real estate is limited.","pack_size":"","size_variables":["2.9mm"],"created_at":"2026-03-26T13:21:05.191553+00:00","updated_at":"2026-03-26T14:44:34.045379+00:00","division_canonical":"